The paper discusses a machine learning approach that involves real-time crowdsourcing to improve accuracy over time. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The specific tasks mentioned in the paper, such as named-entity recognition, sentiment classification, and image classification, suggest that the paper could also fall under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
